data.description: BY FAR THE BEST VALUE IN THE AREA!!!!  SELLER IS READY TO GO!!! NEW FLOORS! NEW PAINT! IT LOOKS LIKE A BRAND-NEW HOME!!!! The seller wanted everything to be perfect, so we replaced all carpet with high-end vinyl  plank. Professionally painted & staged. Nestled on a quiet cul-de-sac, it’s hard to believe this waterfront beauty is so close to so much! Absolutely turn-key & pristine from top-to-bottom, not one detail was overlooked. The super popular open floorplan makes this four-bedroom home feel open & spacious. The custom garage screen door adds so much additional function to the large garage. With all the amazing amenities in this super popular community, it’s truly like being on vacation every single day.
